Jesse Kornbluth, author and editor 
of HeadButler.com, says  Barnes & Noble Inc. (BKS)  is at a crossroads 
due to a "series of unforced errors." Kornbluth talked with 
Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and  Carol Massar  on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Taking Stock" on July 10th.    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 07:31
 